HEADWORD: Pillworm
<hw>Pill"worm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any myriapod of the genus <gen>Iulus</gen> and allied genera which
rolls up spirally; a galleyworm. See <xex>Illust.</xex> under
<er>Myriapod</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pillwort</ent>⟦br⟧
